The well known <b>Stepping Stones</b> across the River Rothey between Ambleside and Pelter Bridge on the Under Loughrigg Road. 

Looking at many of the <a href="http://www.flickr.com/search/?q=Stepping-Stones, Ambleside">Flickr photographs</a> of the Stepping Stones, it seems what time of year you visit determines how dry (or wet) your 'stepping' will be!

